data.description: *Qualifies for $10,000 Own in Ogden Grant, $15,000 for Ogden City Employees and $20,000 for Ogden City Firefighters / Police Officers. Use for down payment, closing costs or principal reduction.* Off 20th St on Ogden's East Bench and close to Ogden Canyon is the quit community of East Grove.  Homes rarely come on the market in this community.  End unit with incredible mountain views. Located at end of community with plenty of parking and open common areas. You will love the peaceful, private covered deck and patio. Main level features 2 large bedrooms (including master) family room, dining and kitchen along with a gas fireplace. Plenty of room downstairs featuring an oversized family room, bedroom, bathroom, office and plenty of storage. HOA covers lawn care,  exterior of homes, and snow maintenance. Easy walk to the Local Transit and UTA Ski Bus for access to Powder Mountain, Snowbasin and Nordic Valley Resorts.  Pineview lake, El Monte and Wolf Creek golf courses and shopping are all close by.
